&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calling all Registered General Nurses &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for something different for the next step in your career?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Something that builds on all the knowledge and skills you already have?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An opportunity to be part of an excellent team that is &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Committed to delivering excellent patient care, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excited to innovate to improve the way different services work together and &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Passionate about having an amazing place to work for all the team &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Then this opportunity has your name on it.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mid and South Essex have embarked on a journey drawing together the expertise in Acute and Community settings to create a truly joined up service for the older population –&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From the community services working directly with GP’s , the hot clinics with geriatrician advice to all professionals and seeing people quickly all helping to keep people at home to a joined up frailty and Intermediate care service at Brentwood Community Hospital and out into all bed based community settings .&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a partnership approach involving doctors, therapists, nurses, administrators, support services from all providers to really make a difference together &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are together calling you for this unique opportunity to come and work in Mid and South Essex Partnership with any of our partner services &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mid and South Essex NHS Foundation Trust ( Basildon, Southend and Broomfield Hospitals)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;North East London NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
